headline: Autodesk CEO talks industry impact of new AI architecture tools
summary: Autodesk (ADSK) CEO and president Andrew Anagnost joins Julie Hyman on Market Catalysts to discuss the company's new AI offerings and how the tech will shape the design and architecture software space. headline: Will Eaton’s (ETN) New Digital Partnerships Reshape Its Competitive Edge in Energy Management?
summary: In recent days, Eaton announced collaborations with Autodesk and Xendee to advance digital energy twin capabilities, microgrid optimization, and AI-powered energy solutions for buildings and data centers, alongside an industry-first innovation targeting power fluctuations in AI computing infrastructure.
